name: Sasha Homes
text: This pizza was amazing. I highly recommend. I liked how you could put any toppings you want and any amount. I also liked how you could choose the size of the pizza and the crust. The desserts were also very good.

name: Shannon Long
text: Took two hours to deliver a medium pizza and breadsticks. The sauce made a whole in my breadsticks and the pizza had some sort of heavy object on top because the cheese stuck to the box when I opened it. The crust was plain, no garlic topping.

name: Mohd Mostafa
text: I had made a wrong order and the pizza was on its way.  I called the store and they modified my order and sent me the one I wanted for my guests. thank you so much for your help and understanding in the last minute.

name: UnlimitedTimeOnly
text: This Pizza Hut seems to be one of the better ones in the area. The pizzas usually turn out better and more consistent that other locations. Orders are done quickly and counter service is quick and friendly.

name: Jermaine Tyler
text: Tracker stated pizza would arrive at one time, only to find out it the delivery driver was no where near my home. Called the store and all they offered was a discount whenever it arrived. I requested refund. However no apologies or a voucher. Poor Customer Service and Delivery Service.

name: GoodBuddyBorf
text: The food is alright. I don’t like the customer service. I waited almost 10 minutes on hold to place my order, and I waited 2 hours for delivery. It wasn’t until I called again when they came. 3 stars for food, 1 star for service

name: Pramésh Gautam
text: I may not have all the best pizza's of the world..but of all the ones I had, these guys make the best pizza. I have ordered and eaten at several other pizza locations, but this particular location has the best pizza making folks working …More

name: Johnny Joestar
text: Not a true Pizza Hut restaurant.  No salad bar and no beer.  The beer thing may be because of it being on Maryland.  The menu was very limited and the server was not very friendly.  We would have had a better experience taking it home.

name: Destiny Bell
text: Great pizza! Young lady was very nice! One of the best pizzas I've had in a while. I will inform my job as well.
